Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.73,0:38:42.15,Commentary,,0,0,0,,水岛 一次都没被认出来
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.73,0:38:45.07,Commentary-up,,0,0,0,,※上冈小学旧址
